••••auviously.squarespace.com•••• S U N D A Y June 4th 2017 : I will be opening to everyone my first baby my first big project the beginning of my brand that I've managed to create with the help from the minds of some amazing people. I've been working hard on this for the past year and it's something Ive always been super passionate about. So many things I've experienced that I've wanted to share from the music I listen to , traveling I'm beginning to do, relationships not a lot but ones that have helped me grow and learn, makeup the most recent love I've encountered this past year that's taking all my money lol. 
It's taken a while for me to get this started but with everything going in my life I figured why not start my own brand and create a space for me to express how I feel in the most epic way. Thank you to Cassandra from Etsy that made my logo and some awesome friends who have helped me with the final tweaks and finishes to make my website whole. Be on the look out everyone June 4, 2017 click the link in my bio and enjoy !  Happy Wednesday 😊
